= SDL_GetMouseState =
Use this function to retrieve the current state of the specified mouse.


== Syntax ==
```c++
Uint8 SDL_GetMouseState(int* x,
                        int* y)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''x'''
|the x coordinate of the mouse cursor position
|-
|'''y'''
|the y coordinate of the mouse cursor position
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns an 8 bit button bitmask of the current button state. ???

